description:
Implement JournalEntry enum per ADR-005:
- Run { name, input, output }
- Sleep { duration_ms, fire_at }
- WaitForSignal { name, payload }
- GetState { key, value }
- SetState { key, value }
- Choice { condition, branch }
- Parallel { branches, results }
- Complete { output }
- Error { error_type, message }
- Serialize/Deserialize with JSON
Acceptance: All step types can be journaled and replayed

Implement full StateConfig enum per ADR-004:
- Pass { result, result_path }
- Task { resource, timeout, heartbeat, retry, catch }
- Wait { seconds, timestamp }
- Choice { choice, default }
- Parallel { branches, retry, catch }
- Map { iterator, items_path, max_concurrency, retry, catch }
- Succeed { output }
- Fail { error, cause }

#[serde(tag = "Type")] for JSON discrimination
Acceptance: All Step Functions state types supported

Implement WfError per ADR-010:
- WorkflowNotFound { workflow }
- InvocationNotFound { invocation_id }
- StepNotFound { step, workflow }
- InvalidTransition { message }
- WorkflowFailed { reason }
- ActivityNotFound { activity }
- ActivityTimeout { activity, timeout_secs }
- ActivityFailed { activity, error }
- MaxRetriesExceeded { attempts, activity }
- CaughtError { error_type, message, next_state }
- Storage (sled::Error)
- Serialization (serde_json::Error)
- AtCapacity { running, max }

thiserror for derive, Serialize, Display
Acceptance: All workflow errors are typed and actionable
